{%- comment -%}
  UNIQUE NUMBER
  Uses a counter to create a unique number.
  Useful when using the same snippet in multiple
  areas of the site.

  Optional variables:
  - prefix
    Define a string to be used before the number
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign counter = counter | default: 0 | plus: 1 -%}
{{- 'now' | date: '%N' | append: counter | prepend: prefix -}}
{%- assign prefix = '' -%}
